Singer Aituaje Iruobbe AKA Waje has taken to her instagram @officialwaje handle to reveal the identity of her lover. He is Ikechukwu Eric Ahiauzu AKA Ric Hassani, also a singer, songwriter and musician. She revealed a picture of herself and her lover with a caption, “it’s time” In response to this, her friend and colleague Omawumi, posted a picture of the duo with a caption: “Besto Asoebi Loading ehhhhh! Congratulations guys @officialwaje,” she wrote.